{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/SteamAboutThisSection_about-this.png?t=1737982903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Arrogue is a deckbuilding roguelike where you will fight against dangerous enemies in turn-per-turn physics-based combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To win you\u2019ll have to collect and upgrade powerful arrows and relics and make wise choices in random events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you die it\u2019s game over: you\u2019ll have to restart from the beginning.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/Combat_Gif_Steam_Page_2.gif?t=1737982903\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/SteamAboutThisSection_features.png?t=1737982903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/Characters_big_with_names.png?t=1737982903\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose the character that suits you the best and go on an adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight against powerful enemies and bosses in a turn-per-turn physics-based combat style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect, upgrade and unlock powerful arrows and relics to protect and restore your village</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore procedurally generated maps and make decisive choices in random events that can lead you to victory or make you restart from the beginning</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Content:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100+ relics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40+ arrows</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_par